channel.title: Need some help with cache suite
channel.description:
Need some help with cache suite.
Open Runescape cache Suite V0.17 BETA by tom.
File > Load Cache... >My Client Files > Cache > .file_store_32 > Open > View/Edit Image Archives > Media > Ok - Now Nothing dsnt work no window pops up with media files and other things ... idk why , last 3 weeks was working....
File > Load Cache... >My Client Files > Cache > .mpr_file_store_32 > Open > View/Edit Image Archives > Media > Ok - Still nothing .....
Why ?
Please Reply , I really need some help here.

item.title: Need some help with cache suite

item.description:
@wonderspring wrote:

trytohaxme:

Once you get to the folder named “cache” click open don’t go into the cache folder then you can edit the image archives.

That dddnt work

[quote=“Rich, post:2, topic:301000”]Try loading a different cache, if it works, then your cache is damaged.[/quote] Yea with another cache it works.Thanks Rich , my cache was damaged.
